优秀的89首歌曲”中名列第87位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rocklists.com/89x-1999.html |title=89X's "Top 89 Songs of 1999 |publisher=Rocklists.com |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518141619/http://www.rocklists.com/89x-1999.html |archivedate=2013-05-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，还在Q101的“1999年最优秀的101首歌曲”中名列第100位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rocklists.com/q101-1999.html |title=Q101's "Top 101 of 1999 |publisher=Rocklists.com |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518165143/http://www.rocklists.com/q101-1999.html |archivedate=2013-05-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

==发行和反响==
《黑日危机》于1999年11月19日在美国[[首演|首映]]，1999年11月26日在英国上映<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1999/11/99/shaken_not_stirred/524858.stm |title=Bond 19: More than enough |publisher=BBC News |date=1999-11-19 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112092225/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1999/11/99/shaken_not_stirred/524858.stm |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。当时米高梅和MTV公司签订了一份市场推广合作计划，主要针对的是美国青少年，并认为这一目标观众群会将邦德视为“老一辈的秘密间谍”。结果MTV在电影发行后马上播放了超过100[[小时|小时]]与邦德有关的节目，其中大部分都以丹妮丝·理查兹为卖点<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1999/11/99/shaken_not_stirred/525210.stm |title=Selling a super spy |publisher=BBC News |date=1999-11-19 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112092315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1999/11/99/shaken_not_stirred/525210.stm |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

影片上映首周就以3551万9007美元的收入登上北美电影票房排列榜冠军宝座，最终在美国进账1亿2694万3684美元，全球票房3亿6183万2400美元<ref name="boxoffice">{{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=worldisnotenough.htm |title=The World Is Not Enough |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325133404/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=worldisnotenough.htm |archivedate=2013-03-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，创下了詹姆斯·邦德电影票房的新纪录，直到《[[新鐵金剛之不日殺機|新鐵金剛之不日殺機]]》上映后才被超越<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=jamesbond.htm |title=James Bond movies |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425021541/http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=jamesbond.htm |archivedate=2013-04-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影还参加[[第72届奥斯卡金像奖|第72届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳视觉效果奖|视觉效果奖]]的第一轮角逐，但没能获得提名<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://commanderbond.net/article/10 |title=TWINE Could Be Up for an Oscar |work=Commanderbond.net |date=2000-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206013828/http://commanderbond.net/article/10 |archivedate=2008-12-06 |accessdate=2008-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《黑日危机》获得了[[土星獎|土星獎]]最佳动作/历险/惊悚电影奖提名，皮尔斯·布鲁斯南赢得了帝国奖和大片娱乐奖的最佳男演员奖，大卫·阿诺德获得了一项BMI电影音乐奖。不过，丹妮丝·理查兹被授予了1999年[[金酸莓奖|金酸莓奖]]最差女配角奖，让本片成为第一部获得这一奖项“肯定”的邦德系列电影。理查兹和布鲁斯南还被提名“最差银幕情侣”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0143145/awards |title=Awards for The World Is Not Enough |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003022840/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0143145/awards |archivedate=2012-10-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

《黑日危机》于2000年5月16日发行了[[DVD|DVD]]，其中包含《007的秘密》（{{lang|en|Secrets of 007}}）花絮内容，电影拍摄的纪录片，两条评论音轨——一条由导演解说，另一条由艺术指导、助理导演和作曲家解说，还有同名游戏的预告片和垃圾合唱团的音乐视频<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.timefordvd.com/SR_TheWorldIsNotEnough.html |title=The World Is Not Enough DVD review |publisher=TimeForDVD.com |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603061308/http://www.timefordvd.com/SR_TheWorldIsNotEnough.html |archivedate=2013-06-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2006年发行的旗舰版DVD中包括一部名为《邦德鸡尾酒》（{{lang|en|Bond Cocktail}}）的2000年纪录片，皮尔斯·布鲁斯南在[[香港|香港]]的一场记者招待会、删除镜头以及向[[戴斯蒙·李維林|戴斯蒙·李維林]]致敬的段落<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://jamesbond.ugo.com/movies/twine/index.php?p=dvd |title=The World Is Not Enough DVD & Soundtrack |publisher=UGO |accessdate=2008-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071121130054/http://jamesbond.ugo.com/movies/twine/index.php?p=dvd |archivedate=2007-11-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

电影获得的评价褒贬不一。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的120篇评论文章，其中61篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为51%，平均得分5.7（最高10分）<ref name="rt">{{Cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/world_is_not_enough/ |title=The World Is Not Enough |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522100337/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/world_is_not_enough/ |archivedate=2013-05-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的33篇评论中则有18篇给出好评，1篇差评，14篇褒贬不一，平均得分59（满分100）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-world-is-not-enough |title=The World Is Not Enough |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003151144/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-world-is-not-enough |archivedate=2012-10-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》影评人[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]给出了三星半的评价（最高四星），认为影片精彩纷呈，刺激而优雅，并且不断给人惊喜<ref name="ebert-review">{{Cite web|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-world-is-not-enough-1999 |title=The World is Not Enough |first=Roger |last=Ebert |work=Chicago Sun-Times |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602181051/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-world-is-not-enough-1999 |archivedate=2013-06-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而对电影的批评则主要针对于剧情的处理和动作场面过多上<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/05/16/world-is-not-enough-the |title=The World Is Not Enough (DVD) review |author=Matt Venendaal |publisher=IGN |date=2006-05-16 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928031722/http://dvd.ign.com/articles/037/037271p1.html |archivedate=2011-09-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》认为这是史上最差的邦德电影，认为其剧情是“如此令人费解，甚至皮尔斯·布鲁斯南也要承认感到迷惑”<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Benjamin Svetkey, Joshua Rich |date=2006-11-15 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1560072_2,00.html |title=Countdown: Ranking the Bond Films |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603044457/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1560072_2%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[MSN|MSN]]的诺曼·威尔纳（{{lang|en|Norman Wilner}}）认为这不是最差，而是第3差，另外两部更差的分别是《[[鐵金剛勇戰大狂魔|鐵金剛勇戰大狂魔]]》和《[[鐵金剛勇戰殺人狂魔|鐵金剛勇戰殺人狂魔]]》<ref>{{Cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080119210839/http://movies.sympatico.msn.ca/features/ArticleNormanWilner.aspx?cp-documentid=436189 |archivedate=2008-01-19 |url=http://movies.sympatico.msn.ca/features/ArticleNormanWilner.aspx?cp-documentid=436189 |title=Rating the Spy Game |publisher=MSN |author=Norman Wilner |accessdate=2008-01-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。而[[IGN|IGN]]网站则认为这是史上第5烂的邦德电影<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/11/17/james-bonds-top-20 |title=James Bond's Top 20 |publisher=IGN |date=2006-11-17 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002033042/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/11/17/james-bonds-top-20 |archivedate=2012-10-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

评论家批评让理查兹来扮演一个核科学家实在缺乏可信度<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Lisanti|first=Tom|last2=Paul|first2=Louis|year=2002|title=Film Fatales: Women in Espionage Films and Television, 1962–1973|publisher=McFarland & Co|location=Jefferson, NC|isbn=978-0-7864-1194-8|postscript=<!--None-->}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Howe, Desson |date=1999-11-19 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/entertainment/movies/reviews/worldisnotenoughhowe.htm |title='World': Bond without end |publisher=''Washington Post'' |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729080258/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/entertainment/movies/reviews/worldisnotenoughhowe.htm |archive-date=2013-07-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的服装——背心和短裤也招来了类似的反应<ref>{{Cite news|last=Herincx |first=Gareth |date=1999-11-19 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1999/11/99/shaken_not_stirred/524858.stm |title=Bond 19: More than enough |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112092225/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1999/11/99/shaken_not_stirred/524858.stm |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2008年，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》将丹妮丝·理查兹评为史上最糟糕的[[邦德女郎|邦德女郎]]之一<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Rich |first=Joshua |date=2008-01-08 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20170028,00.html#1240410 |title=James Bond Babes: Best and Worst |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607183459/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20170028%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

==改编==
邦德小说家{{link-en|雷蒙德·本森|Raymond Benson}}根据电影的剧本创作了同名改编小说，部分细节有所改动，比如邦德的武器仍然是[[瓦爾特PP手槍|瓦爾特PP手槍]]而不是更新款的P99等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fantasticfiction.co.uk/b/raymond-benson/world-is-not-enough.htm|title=Reymond Benson - The World Is Not Enough|publisher=Fantastic Fiction|date=|accessdate=2013-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131119030508/http://www.fantasticfiction.co.uk/b/raymond-benson/world-is-not-enough.htm|archive-date=2013-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2000年，[[美国艺电|美国艺电]]根据本片创作了基于[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]和[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]平台的同名[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]。不过之后针对[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]和[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]版本的发布计划予以取消，这些版本本有望使用[[Id_Tech_3引擎|Id Tech 3]][[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]<ref>Black Ops had previously adapted ''Tomorrow Never Dies'' for the PlayStation and would go on to develop ''Nightfire'' in 2002.</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/04/27/the-world-is-not-enough-6 |title=The World Is Not Enough preview (PS2) |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120714042506/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/134/134285p1.html |archivedate=2012-07-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

